{"tid":1907423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★相隔16秒上同一架巴士 事主坐近患者零交流 因對方一個動作中招","createTime":"2020-03-02T15:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T15:11:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cb63102613b7203ad2b4cf818558f569a9e4eb31","tid":1907423,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T15:00:31.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2575000/2578623/WhatsAp_1024.jpeg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2575000%2F2578623%2FWhatsAp_1024.jpeg&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=1413c2e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2575000/2578623/WhatsAp_1024.jpeg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n新冠肺炎（武漢肺炎）疫情持續蔓延，重慶一名65歲男子早前搭巴士時未有佩戴口罩，與另一名確診者前後相隔16秒登上同一輛巴士，更與對方坐得接近，疑在途中受到感染。<br />\n<br />\n江北區疾控中心副主任醫生周海龍，於上月28日公布一宗重慶的病例，患者為一名65歲男子，於1月23日出現流鼻涕、乏力等症狀，1月30日到醫院就診，院方將其列為新冠肺炎疑似病例，惟3次檢測結果都是呈陰性，至上月5日才確診，血液和糞便樣本檢測結果呈陽性。<br />\n<br />\n由於該名男子的活動史非常簡單，發病前14天均甚少外出，除了每天早上出門乘坐巴士去健身、中午就回家外，只出席過一次朋友聚會，惟聚會上所有接觸者經檢測後結果全是呈陰性。<br />\n<br />\n及後當局終透過車上長者卡的拍卡記錄，發現事主曾於1月19日早上在一輛巴士上與另一名確診者相遇，事主出門坐巴士去健身，另一名確診者剛巧也坐巴士前往看症，2人前後相差16秒登上同一輛巴士。<br />\n<br />\n根據車上的閉路電視顯示，事主當時坐在確診者的斜後方，並沒有佩戴口罩。雖然該名確診者有戴上口罩，但中途曾把口罩除下，加上當時車窗都是關閉的，懷疑事主因此受到感染。<br />\n<br />\n周海龍提醒，市民乘搭公共交通工具時，一定要佩戴口罩，同時亦要提醒身邊的人戴好口罩，在車上盡量不要周圍觸摸物件，下車後要盡快消毒雙手<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2578623/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E7%9B%B8%E9%9A%9416%E7%A7%92%E4%B8%8A%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%9E%B6%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%20%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E5%9D%90%E8%BF%91%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E9%9B%B6%E4%BA%A4%E6%B5%81%20%E5%9B%A0%E5%B0%8D%E6%96%B9%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E5%8B%95%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AD%E6%8B%9B#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2578623%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%259B%25B8%25E9%259A%259416%25E7%25A7%2592%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%259E%25B6%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%2520%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%259D%2590%25E8%25BF%2591%25E6%2582%25A3%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%259B%25B6%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%25B5%2581%2520%25E5%259B%25A0%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E4%25BD%259C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%258B%259B%23%26gid%3D1%26pid%3D1&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=889ca1be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2578623/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E7%9B%B8%E9%9A%9416%E7%A7%92%E4%B8%8A%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E6%9E%B6%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%20%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E5%9D%90%E8%BF%91%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E9%9B%B6%E4%BA%A4%E6%B5%81%20%E5%9B%A0%E5%B0%8D%E6%96%B9%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E5%8B%95%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%AD%E6%8B%9B#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=1</a>"},{"pid":"40aeba6e8fa33e959239d749e2aade133a27c905","tid":1907423,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T15:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.lih.kg/540/https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2575000/2578623/WhatsAp_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.lih.kg%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2575000%2F2578623%2FWhatsAp_1024.jpeg&h=3571760d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4104e3f731bc4e12f1f8fe673a84438bd55b8c90","tid":1907423,"uid":33874,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T15:11:43.000Z","msg":"垃圾標題黨<br />\n乜春16秒<br />\n坐撚咗成程車仲要條友無口罩<br />\n係唔係哩到中都唔知啦"}]}